node.title: Worker dies on building site in Perth's southern suburbs
node.alt: The silhouettes of two people inside a Perth Airport terminal with Virgin planes outside the window.
node.description: A man dies while working on a residential building site in North Coogee in Perth's south, after he is believed to have been struck on the head.
node.content: ["A man has died while working on a residential building site in Perth's southern suburbs.", "It is\u00a0understood the man was struck on the head and died at the site in North Coogee this morning.", "Police were called to the building site\u00a0on Reinforcement Parade just before 10:00am.", "Worksafe has launched an\u00a0investigation.", "More to come."]
